<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-19 10:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1464 &Cx1f; tad-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-US-MEXICO-$ADV21-COX     02-19 1909
</HEADER>
<BODY>
