<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-19 10:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1502 &Cx1f; tad-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MCCARTY-COLUMN20-COX     02-19 0925
