   JOEMURRAY-COLUMN _ The president wants to send peacekeeping
troops to Kosovo. Opposition is being expressed by the Congress.
The Congress is right. Who among us can even find Kosovo on the
map? (Murray, Cox News Service) MOVED THURSDAY.
