the governor's leadership skills, critics claim he has little
chance of succeeding. (Working.) Hurt
</P>
<P>
   WYOMING -- RENO. Sen. Craig Thomas will ask Attorney General
Janet Reno to investigate whether meat-packing companies have
illegally depressed prices for farm products, he announced
Thursday. (Filed at 12:45.) Davant
</P>
