<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Saturday, Feb. 20,
1999.
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDs: Adds: CLINTON-MEDIA, BANKER-SHOOTS-SON. Deletes: CLINTON,
