<P>
   WORKPLACE-COLUMN-SMITH (Undated) _ Your mother was right. If you
don't eat your vegetables, you won't get dessert. You can't judge a
book by its cover. Sharing is caring. It turns out that a mother's
intuition makes good sense in business as well. It took Rhonda
Abrams, a small-business consultant and author of ``Wear Clean
