<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-KOSOVO-U.S.-ART-725&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CLINTON INCREASES PRESSURE ON MILOSEVIC AS DEADLINE NEARS 
</HEADLINE>
 
(REPEATING to add photo note)  
 (ATTN: France, Great Britain)  (Eds: See also KOSOVO-TALKS, KOSOVO-MOOD) 
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
may make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(mk) 
 By ELIZABETH BECKER   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
