<DOCNO> NYT19990219.0356 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-19 21:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2250 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JILLS-HYSTERECTOMY-LA     02-19 1072
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JILLS-HYSTERECTOMY-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`HOME IMPROVEMENT' DEALS WITH ISSUE, FEAR OF HYSTERECTOMY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
(Attn: For use Monday, Feb. 22 or thereafter). 
 
  
By BETTY KWONG  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
  
