<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-19 22:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2324 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPACE-PORT-HNS &LR;      02-19 0941
